        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Greenhouse gas Reduction and Environmental Enhancement through New Ferries Act or the GREEN Ferries Act</strong></p> <p>This bill makes projects to construct or otherwise acquire zero- or reduced-emissions passenger ferries (and related facilities and equipment) eligible for grants that support transit capital, operating assistance, and transportation planning in urbanized areas.</p>]]>
        </text>
